+/**
+ * Claude CLI with --output-format json wraps its response in an envelope:
+ *   { type: "result", result: "<actual text>", total_cost_usd: 0.001, ... }
+ *
+ * We unwrap it so callers always receive the raw Claude text in `stdout`.
